    BasePackageListAction, BaseSetListAction, ChannelSystemsAction, CompareChannelAction, CompareCopyAction, CompareFileAction, CompareRevisionAction, ConfigConfirmAction, DiffFilesAction, DiffSystemsAction, FileListConfirmSetupAction, GlobalConfigFileList, GlobalRevisionDeployConfirmSetup, LocalConfigFileList, SummaryAction, SystemChannelsAction, UnsubscribeConfirmAction

    public abstract class BaseListAction
extends RhnListAction
    BaseListAction - basic base class you can extend to provide functionality for generating a list with support for precondition checking, and setup for building the pageList attribute on the Request. Meant for lists without RhnSet selections.

      • checkPreConditions

        protected java.lang.String checkPreConditions(RequestContext rctx)
        Override if you want to check a precondition before executing this Action. If the precondition fails and returns a NON-NULL return value this will be used as a Resource key for an error message will forward the request to the "error" ActionForward.
        Parameters:
        rctx - the context of the current request
        Returns:
        String key for an error message.
